net.objectzoo.events.impl

Interface EventDelegate<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the information parameter the event provides
    All Superinterfaces:
    Action<T>, java.util.function.Consumer<T>, Event<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EventAsyncDelegate<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EventAsyncAdapter, EventCaller, EventDistributor

    public interface EventDelegate<T>
extends Action<T>, Event<T>
    An EventDelegate implements Action as well as Event and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the Action interface to all subscribers of the Event interface.

    tilmann
